{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1e9b6f4-2c1a-4b7e-9c3a-5f6d8e0a1b2c",
    "name": "TaxVision - PaymentApp",
    "description": "Colección de pruebas del microservicio PaymentApp de TaxVision (cobra a los tenants por su propia suscripción SaaS). Usa el environment TaxVisionBackEnd (variable UrlBase apuntando al Gateway, p. ej. http://localhost:5047). La mayoría de endpoints requieren TenantAdmin (o el rol con los permisos payment_app.* correspondientes); la carpeta Admin requiere PlatformAdmin (permiso payment_app.admin.cross_tenant). Los webhooks de Stripe son públicos y verifican HMAC — sin un evento real de Stripe (p. ej. via `stripe listen --forward-to`) responderán 400 por firma inválida, lo cual es el comportamiento esperado.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "SaaSPayments",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GetSaaSPaymentById",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/payments-app/saas-payments/{{saaSPaymentId}}",
              "host": ["{{UrlBase}}"],
              "path": ["payments-app", "saas-payments", "{{saaSPaymentId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Detalle de un SaaSPayment del tenant autenticado (scoped por TenantId). Requiere payment_app.saas_payment.read."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "RefundSaaSPayment",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refundAmountCents\": 500,\n  \"reason\": \"cliente solicito reembolso parcial\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/payments-app/saas-payments/{{saaSPaymentId}}/refund",
              "host": ["{{UrlBase}}"],
              "path": ["payments-app", "saas-payments", "{{saaSPaymentId}}", "refund"]
            },
            "description": "Reembolso administrativo, solo plataforma (un tenant nunca se reembolsa a si mismo). Requiere payment_app.saas_payment.refund. Falla si excede el invariante SumOfRefunds + newRefund <= Amount."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "ProviderCustomers",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GetProviderCustomer",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const c = pm.response.json();\r",
                  "if (c && c.id) {\r",
                  "    pm.environment.set('tenantProviderCustomerId', c.id);\r",
                  "    console.log('tenantProviderCustomerId:', c.id);\r",
                  "}\r"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/payments-app/provider-customers/Stripe",
              "host": ["{{UrlBase}}"],
              "path": ["payments-app", "provider-customers", "Stripe"]
            },
            "description": "Customer del tenant en Stripe (con sus SavedMethods) para pagos de la suscripcion SaaS. Requiere payment_app.provider_customer.read. Se provisiona automaticamente al crear el tenant (§D.4)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "AttachPaymentMethod",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const methodId = pm.response.json();\r",
                  "if (methodId) {\r",
                  "    pm.environment.set('providerMethodId', methodId);\r",
                  "    console.log('providerMethodId:', methodId);\r",
                  "}\r"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"paymentMethodReference\": \"pm_card_visa\",\n  \"setAsDefault\": true\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/payments-app/provider-customers/Stripe/methods",
              "host": ["{{UrlBase}}"],
              "path": ["payments-app", "provider-customers", "Stripe", "methods"]
            },
            "description": "El frontend ya tokenizo la tarjeta con Stripe Elements/SetupIntent; este endpoint solo recibe la referencia opaca (nunca PAN crudo). pm_card_visa es el payment method de test que expone Stripe para pegarle a la API sin pasar por Elements. Requiere payment_app.provider_customer.manage. Devuelve el Guid del metodo guardado."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "DetachPaymentMethod",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/payments-app/provider-customers/{{tenantProviderCustomerId}}/methods/{{providerMethodId}}",
              "host": ["{{UrlBase}}"],
              "path": ["payments-app", "provider-customers", "{{tenantProviderCustomerId}}", "methods", "{{providerMethodId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Desasocia un metodo de pago guardado. Requiere payment_app.provider_customer.manage."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "SetDefaultPaymentMethod",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/payments-app/provider-customers/{{tenantProviderCustomerId}}/methods/{{providerMethodId}}/default",
              "host": ["{{UrlBase}}"],
              "path": ["payments-app", "provider-customers", "{{tenantProviderCustomerId}}", "methods", "{{providerMethodId}}", "default"]
            },
            "description": "Marca un metodo guardado como default para cobros futuros (renovaciones, dunning). Requiere payment_app.provider_customer.manage."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin (PlatformAdmin)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "SearchAllTenantsPayments",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/payments-app/admin/payments?page=1&pageSize=50",
              "host": ["{{UrlBase}}"],
              "path": ["payments-app", "admin", "payments"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "50" },
                { "key": "status", "value": "Succeeded", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "type", "value": "SubscriptionRenewal", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "from", "value": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "to", "value": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Cross-tenant por diseño (§42.6): sin tenantId trae pagos de TODOS los tenants, incluso suspendidos. Requiere payment_app.admin.cross_tenant (PlatformAdmin lo tiene siempre). No confundir con GetSaaSPaymentById, que esta scoped al tenant del JWT."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "SearchTenantPayments",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/payments-app/admin/tenants/{{tenantId}}/payments?page=1&pageSize=50",
              "host": ["{{UrlBase}}"],
              "path": ["payments-app", "admin", "tenants", "{{tenantId}}", "payments"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "50" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Vista admin de los pagos de UN tenant especifico (incluso si esta suspendido). Requiere payment_app.admin.cross_tenant."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "ExportPaymentsCsv",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/payments-app/admin/payments/export",
              "host": ["{{UrlBase}}"],
              "path": ["payments-app", "admin", "payments", "export"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "tenantId", "value": "{{tenantId}}", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "status", "value": "Succeeded", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Mismos filtros que SearchAllTenantsPayments, sin paginacion (capado a 5000 filas). Devuelve text/csv. Requiere payment_app.admin.cross_tenant."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Webhooks (Stripe - publico)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "StripeWebhook",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" },
              { "key": "Stripe-Signature", "value": "t=1700000000,v1=replace_with_a_real_signature", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"id\": \"evt_test_postman\",\n  \"type\": \"payment_intent.succeeded\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"object\": {\n      \"id\": \"pi_test_postman\"\n    }\n  }\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/payments-app/webhooks/stripe",
              "host": ["{{UrlBase}}"],
              "path": ["payments-app", "webhooks", "stripe"]
            },
            "description": "Publico, sin JWT — Stripe autentica con HMAC en Stripe-Signature. Este body/firma son de ejemplo: con la firma dummy de arriba la respuesta esperada es 400 (Stripe.WebhookSignature.Invalid), NO 500 — eso confirma que la verificacion de firma esta activa. Para probar el flujo completo usa `stripe listen --forward-to {{UrlBase}}/payments-app/webhooks/stripe` y dispara un evento real con `stripe trigger payment_intent.succeeded`. Rate limitado a 1000 req/min/IP (§K.1)."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
